<div class="modalcontainer">
<div class="modalbox">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2><span>著作信息</span></h2>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>驴哥尤利西斯 和 他的窝</strong>，画师：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602049364" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<a href="/scp-4768">最初关于驴哥的文章</a><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<a href="/drakimoto-s-author-page">~DrAkimoto的作者页~</a></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /></p>
<div style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-donkman-s-den/donk1" style="width:75%;" alt="donk1" class="image" /></div>
<h6 id="toc0"><span><strong><em>“如果恁不活好每一分钟，那末俺每就觉得恁没有在活着哩。”</em></strong></span></h6>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span style="font-size:smaller;">– 驴哥尤利西斯</span></p>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="border:solid 1px #999999; background:#FFF8E7; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<h5 id="toc1"><span><strong><a href="/scp-4768">SCP-4768 - 驴哥尤利西斯的大奇事</a></strong></span></h5>
<p><strong>作者：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602049364" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span></strong></p>
<h6 id="toc2"><span><em>那家伙，那怪谈，总之故事就开始了。</em></span></h6>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>
<h3 id="toc3"><span>最伟大的奇事：</span></h3>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div style="border:solid 1px #999999; background:#FFF8E7; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/9b/Train_Icon_bw.svg" style="height:75px; width:75px; padding-left: 0%;" /></p>
<h5 id="toc4"><span><strong><a href="/ulysses-b-donkman-and-the-clockwork-bandits">尤利西斯与时钟怪盗</a></strong></span></h5>
<p><strong>作者：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602049364" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span> 和 <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4916887); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602049364" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4916887); return false;">MalyceGraves</a></span></strong></p>
<h6 id="toc5"><span><em>在嘟嘟火车大劫案中对峙螺栓匪徒们的驴哥是否搞错了什么！</em></span></h6>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="border:solid 1px #999999; background:#FFF8E7; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><img src="http://kontainer.djkakt.us/local--files/the-funeral/1582572222984.png" style="height:75px; width:70px; padding-left: 0%;" /></p>
<h5 id="toc6"><span><strong><a href="/ulysses-b-donkman-and-the-heinous-hitman">尤利西斯与极恶杀手</a></strong></span></h5>
<p><strong>作者：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5045819); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5045819&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602049364" alt="Calibri Bold" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5045819)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5045819); return false;">Calibri Bold</a></span></strong></p>
<h6 id="toc7"><span><em>夭寿啦！驴哥你真的没被收走吗？</em></span></h6>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="border:solid 1px #999999; background:#FFF8E7; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-donkman-s-den/Grave_icon.png" style="height:75px; width:70px; padding-left: 0%;" /></p>
<h5 id="toc8"><span><strong><a href="/ulysses-b-donkman-and-the-mournful-birthday">尤利西斯与悲怆诞辰</a></strong></span></h5>
